quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  5,32,"Eshichila ako, nikhuhandichila Abana ba Israili mbu, “Ulia ulera omundu eshikhaya bustwa omundu oyo nalerere omundu tawe, nohomba okhukhola obutobela khushialo, alaba shinga wirire abandu boosi. Ne ulia uwonokosia omundu, ali shinga uwonokosiye obandu boosi." Ne toto Abarumwa befu babeetsela nende ebifune bili habulafu. Mana abanji mubo olunyuma lwa ako nibaba abeyisasia."
  5,33,"Toto omurungo kwa balia bakhupananga nende Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, nende okhukhola obwononia khushialo; ni okhwirwa, nohomba okhubambwa, nohomba okhutetwa emikhono chiabu nende ebilenje buchikha, nohomba balondwe mushialo esho. Esho neshifimbwa murwe shiabu khushialo, ne mwikulu balinyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo."
  5,34,"Halali balia abasaba eshileshelo nimushili okhubatila. Ne manye mbu Nyasaye ni wobulesheli po, wetsimbabaasi muno."
  5,35,"Enywe abasuubila, rie Nyasaye ne konye injila yokhumuulilakhwo. Ne lwane shichila Injila yiyie khomunyoole okhubura."
  5,36,"Toto balia bakhaya, babetsanga nende bili mushialo bioosi nende ebindi shinga birio, kho babirusie, kho bakhaya okhunyoola eshinyasio inyanga ya Indukho, shibakhachamilwe tawe. Ne balinyoola eshinyasio shitsuninjia."